Package: hdf5MEA
Type: Package
Title: R I/O Toolkit for Multi-well HDF5 MEA Files (BRW/BXR v4)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Hyojung", "Yoon", 
           email = "hyojungyoon90@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer@R: person("Hyojung", "Yoon", 
           email = "hyojungyoon90@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))           
Description: Read and inspect 3Brain-style BRW/BXR v4 HDF5 files in R.
    Provides reliable loading, partial data extraction, export capabilities, 
    and integration with existing analysis algorithms.
    Supports EventsBasedSparseRaw data format with time-based partial loading and 
    various sparse data handling modes. Designed for memory-efficient
    processing of large-scale multi-electrode array (MEA) electrophysiology data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
